dc_description_s: This point data layer represents buildings/structures for Shawano County, Wisconsin in 2023.[The building points are utilized for general mapping purposes and emergency services to locate the primary structure on a given parcel. The points were placed using the Planning, Development, and Zoning department's address permit forms, and the 2015 orthophotos. Some points were placed with prior orthophotos or placed at the best possible estimate for new construction.]
